name: date
command:
days=['solday','lunday', 'noctday', 'apolloday', 'arteday', 'raeday', 'heliday']
months=['celestuary','bembuary', 'smarch', 'dazzleton', 'zephyrion', 'luminarch', 'jomber', 'blimber']
ordinals=['st','nd','rd']
now=new Date
print(`${days[now.getDay()%days.length]} ${months[now.getMonth()%months.length]} ${IRC.require('fliptext')(String(now.getDate()))}${ordinals[now.getDate()%ordinals.length]} ${now.getFullYear() + 4}`)
